      <title>内塔尼亚胡悬赏每释放一名人质500万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/netanyahu-offers-a-5-million-reward-for-each-hostage-returned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡周二表示，以色列将向任何释放人质的加沙居民支付 500 万美元，并提供安全通道让他们离开这片饱受战争蹂躏的领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/netanyahu-offers-a-5-million-reward-for-each-hostage-returned</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 20:14:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
